{"tid":2509265,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國銀行律師涉襲警案自辯 指警俞樹生當時情緒失控似有精神問題或毒癮","createTime":"2021-04-29T10:00:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-29T13:09:48.000Z","uid":56115,"like":43,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fda9b2186139d47d9a115b362de3b947aa072a1d","tid":2509265,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T10:00:41.000Z","msg":"任職銀行律師的美籍男子，前年在銅鑼灣港鐵站捲入休班警追截懷疑跳閘⻘年的糾紛，被控襲擊休班警，案件今續審。被告今日自辯指，當時覺得跳閘男非常年幼，只是一名孩子（kid），卻遭事主以警棍大力扛著頸項逼向牆邊。被告看見<span class=\"red\">少年貌似窒息</span>，遂上前問事主是否警員，惟事主矢口否認。其後<span class=\"red\">事主更向被告大吼大叫</span>，完全不能控制情緒。被告當時覺得<span class=\"red\">事主神情似有精神問題或毒癮</span>，會危害途人安全，遂捉著事主的警棍。<br />\n<br />\n被告認為少年處於險境，遂<span class=\"red\">以普通話問二人：「你是不是警察？」</span>被告庭上解釋自己不懂得說廣東話，但曾學習普通話。盧回以普通話答謂：「不是。」俞則起初頭也不回，繼續以警棍摃著少年；被告遂再次質問他，此時俞才語氣暴躁地回答：「不是！」由於俞及盧被戴帽男與被告糾纏，最終少年成功逃脫。俞立即緊隨少年離開現場。<br />\n<br />\n未幾俞折返現場，向被告大吼：「What are you doing?」被告形容俞當時雙眼充血，完全不能自我控制，認為俞可能有精神問題（mental health crisis）或毒癮（drug problems），並擔心其狀態或導致周遭途人有危險。<br />\n<br />\n俞的行為絕對不像一名警員應有的作為，故被告當時肯定俞並非警員。聆訊繼續。"},{"pid":"304ead0a71283e7c7d8ef022a3f95ef340ce6424","tid":2509265,"uid":56115,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T10:00:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210429/I42ZMEWPJJBAJAGK63YF6UU3NI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210429%2FI42ZMEWPJJBAJAGK63YF6UU3NI%2F&d=4YJm346n2OvV5E02CjQHwcrrJHX4TENqAnNRziDaZDA%3D&h=b2c39be0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210429%2FI42ZMEWPJJBAJAGK63YF6UU3NI%2F&h=f72f71e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210429/I42ZMEWPJJBAJAGK63YF6UU3NI/</a>"},{"pid":"bac79c4ea54febfedea30863aaa5a8358a74ce44","tid":2509265,"uid":56115,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T10:05:22.000Z","msg":"但在被告與友人走上樓梯時，再次見到俞不斷大喊「What are you doing?」，又一直揮舞長棍，他形容俞當時完全失控，認為俞有精神問題（mental health crisis）或藥物問題，危害身邊市民的安全，於是上前嘗試捉住俞的長棍，以防俞傷害他人。被告指，他嘗試不果後，<span class=\"red\">俞將長棍舉高欲擊向他的頭部，他隨即向後退拉遠二人距離。被告稱，俞突然倒地，同時將他扯到地上，更三度以長棍擊打其臀部及雙腿。</span><a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/%E7%BE%8E%E7%B1%8D%E9%8A%80%E8%A1%8C%E5%BE%8B%E5%B8%AB%E6%B6%89%E8%A5%B2%E4%BC%91%E7%8F%AD%E8%AD%A6-%E8%87%AA%E8%BE%AF%E7%A8%B1%E4%BB%A5%E6%99%AE%E9%80%9A%E8%A9%B1%E5%95%8F-%E4%BD%A0%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%AF%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F-%E4%BC%91%E7%8F%AD%E8%AD%A6%E5%A4%A7%E5%96%8A-%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%AF/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E7%25B1%258D%25E9%258A%2580%25E8%25A1%258C%25E5%25BE%258B%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E6%25B6%2589%25E8%25A5%25B2%25E4%25BC%2591%25E7%258F%25AD%25E8%25AD%25A6-%25E8%2587%25AA%25E8%25BE%25AF%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E6%2599%25AE%25E9%2580%259A%25E8%25A9%25B1%25E5%2595%258F-%25E4%25BD%25A0%25E6%2598%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2598%25AF%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25AF%259F-%25E4%25BC%2591%25E7%258F%25AD%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%2596%258A-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2598%25AF%2F&d=4YJm346n2OvV5E02CjQHwcrrJHX4TENqAnNRziDaZDA%3D&h=c6a8c211\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E7%25B1%258D%25E9%258A%2580%25E8%25A1%258C%25E5%25BE%258B%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E6%25B6%2589%25E8%25A5%25B2%25E4%25BC%2591%25E7%258F%25AD%25E8%25AD%25A6-%25E8%2587%25AA%25E8%25BE%25AF%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E6%2599%25AE%25E9%2580%259A%25E8%25A9%25B1%25E5%2595%258F-%25E4%25BD%25A0%25E6%2598%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2598%25AF%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25AF%259F-%25E4%25BC%2591%25E7%258F%25AD%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%2596%258A-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2598%25AF%2F&h=a8012a6f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/court/%E7%BE%8E%E7%B1%8D%E9%8A%80%E8%A1%8C%E5%BE%8B%E5%B8%AB%E6%B6%89%E8%A5%B2%E4%BC%91%E7%8F%AD%E8%AD%A6-%E8%87%AA%E8%BE%AF%E7%A8%B1%E4%BB%A5%E6%99%AE%E9%80%9A%E8%A9%B1%E5%95%8F-%E4%BD%A0%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%AF%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F-%E4%BC%91%E7%8F%AD%E8